author: Xbox
description:
Spray Paint Simulator is out now on Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, and Xbox Game Pass!

Relax, get creative, and transform items from drab to fab in Spray Paint Simulator. Meet with an eccentric group of clients in Career Mode and grow your business from the ground up! Take on each job right from the start by prepping your space to ensure you deliver the best results, selecting the right colors for the task, and  paint to perfection to keep your customers happy! 

Upgrade your tools, vehicles, and equipment, and use an assortment of ladders and scaffolding to help you get to those hard-to-reach spots. Fill the world with rainbow hues, painting everything from rooms and homes to cars and bridges and even giant robots! Unlock Free Spray mode and dive in alone or with a friend to make the entire town your canvas and unleash your creative freedom!

Spray Paint Simulator is available on Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, and PC via the Microsoft Store now. 

The game is available day one with Xbox Gam
title: Spray Paint Simulator - Out Now | Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, Xbox Game Pass

author: Xbox
description:
Surrounded by murky and perilous waters lies a wicked isle… a mysterious new region to explore, nestled off the Cumberland coast. They say there was a creepy old fishing village out there, but the locals haven’t seen anyone from there for years. 

There is a boat from the Wyndham Village shore for anyone brave enough to go and look for themselves. New mysteries, new supplies and new possibilities of escape could lie ahead for anyone who dares.

The Atomfall story continues with Story Expansion Pack: Wicked Isle, coming to Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, and Windows PC on June 3rd 2025.
 
https://www.xbox.com/games/store/atomfall/9nc4wdl5kzbl


A single-player survival-action game inspired by real-life events, Atomfall is set five years after the Windscale nuclear disaster in Northern England.
